{"tid":1540591,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求，缺一不可！加拿大手足絕不妥協！","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T02:55:05.000Z","uid":23480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1e27c052510edcdd4da81eb79038b32cb326cd","tid":1540591,"uid":23480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QjQDEw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QjQDEw.png&h=71bfa2a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n我們沒有勝利。<br />\n幾十位兄弟，用生命和鮮血換來的。<br />\n不會就這樣結束。<br />\n還記得太子斷頸的兄弟嗎？<br />\n還記得太子失蹤的三位手足嗎？<br />\n還記得831嗎？<br />\n還記得721嗎？<br />\n還記得這個女人兩個月前的暫援嗎？<br />\n還記得我們在憲報上搵到的法案嗎？<br />\n還記得蒙著面殘殺非禮強姦我們的警察嗎？<br />\n一切，並沒有結束。<br />\n一切也沒有改變。<br />\n請我們繼續。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n加港同行 #cansavehk<br />\n我們只會繼續！<br />\n全力支持909美國國會人權法案<br />\n各地將會有活動<br />\n我們加拿大手足，繼續與港同行。<br />\n絕不妥協！<br />\n<br />\n加港同行facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cansavehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcansavehk%2F&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f695424e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cansavehk/</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大公海TG<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/unitedhkcanadian\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Funitedhkcanadian&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=aaa926e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/unitedhkcanadian</a>"},{"pid":"94edd1e8468ad4196da576ce7000b922cdad34bf","tid":1540591,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgdcLSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgdcLSU.jpg&h=7d8fce73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={